"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-lifestyle-celeb-news-local-celebs-olympics-botswana-tebogo-gold-200m-chidimma-miss-sa-latest\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.8001294031471106, \"rank\": 0.2497931526671404, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bb'Hypocrites': SA takes 'credit' for Botswana's Tebogo, after shunning Chidimma  X users are calling out South Africans praising Botswana's gold-medallist Tebogo, hours after celebrating Chidimma's Miss SA exit.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.8001294031471106, \"rank\": 0.2497931526671404, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.383108919106775e-29, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 306, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 380, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.383108919106775e-29, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africans on social media are calling out the \\\"hypocrisy\\\" of others who are celebrating Botswana Olympic sprinter Letsile Tebogo, who won gold in the 200m race on Thursday, 8 August.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This, after seemingly celebrating finalist Chidimma Adetshina's early exit from the Miss SA pageant  The 23-year-old womanannounced her decision to withdraw from the competition,citing concerns for her safety and well-being.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.383108919106775e-29, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past few weeks, Chidimma has made headlines over her African parentage, which includes a Nigerian father and an alleged Mozambican mother.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994040885309392, \"rank\": 0.0005562923576205825, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mozambique\", \"score\": 0.999997700698174, \"rank\": 1.5598396211240797e-06, \"text\": \"Mozambican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mozambique\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mozambique\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Miss SA finale takes place on Saturday, 10 August, at the SunBet Arena in Pretoria.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.383108919106775e-29, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.768920020203e-14, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday, Chidimma Adetshina announced her decision to step down as a Top 10 finalist at the Miss SA pageant.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.383108919106775e-29, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This followed weeks ofsuffering xenophobic and Afrophobic comments on social mediaand even being labelled a \\\"Nigerian.\\\"\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994040885309392, \"rank\": 0.0005562923576205825, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chidimma's announcement came shortly after Minister of Home Affairs Leon Schreiber's statement of a preliminary investigation that claims her mother may have committed fraud and identity theft when registering her birth.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just hours later, Letsile Tebogo of Botswana would win gold in the men's 200m race at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reception of the two Africans by social media users has been polar opposite in comparison.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the X platform, many South Africans celebrated fellow \\\"African\\\" Tebogo, some of which earlier condemned Chidimma as a non-South African.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some even attempted to take credit for having a \\\"Tswana\\\" heritage.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others called out the hypocrisy of the situation.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@CMogoeng:\\\"Tebogo Letsile did it for Botswana, not South Africa.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1992, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 2006, \"end\": 2018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.495797122648204e-17, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not get to be xenophobic and Afrophobic today and then tomorrow claim other people's glory because we are in a good mood and it suits us\\\"  @MR_K_R_B:\\\"Claiming Tebogo after winning Gold on the same day after disowning Chidimma does not look good on us.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@Melo22Taro:\\\"Making Chidimma resign from Miss SA when she grew up here as a child (unbeknownst of her mother's actions) and glorifying a Botswana Olympian gold medalists as if he is South African (clearly not) all within this week is some funny sh*t.\\\"  @angrybird_c:\\\"South Africans are hypocrites.\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2325, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.383108919106775e-29, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 2416, \"end\": 2424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999983651833, \"rank\": 1.6306386650111992e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are quick to show support for Botswana's Tebogo because of his win but could not let Chidimma complete her Miss SA run.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2612, \"end\": 2620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.383108919106775e-29, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's disgusting.\\\"\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Letsile Tebogo has become the first African and athlete from Botswana, to win gold in the Olympics 200m.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999947458491, \"rank\": 5.2541875435945885e-09, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo beat the likes of Noah Lyle, a favourite who later claimed to have contracted Covid-19.\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9996500927855694, \"rank\": 0.00034481402605744384, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The humble 21-year-old claimed that while he appreciated the praise, he was unfazed by the instant fame.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said in apress conferenceafter the race: \\\"It is not a dream come true to me.\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A medal is just a medal - but what I went through.\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would say the medal is a bonus to everybody, but personally, it is not a dream come true.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo dedicated the victory to his mother, who died in May.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"'It is not a big deal to me.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means a lot to the team behind me.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When we heard about my mom's passing, I was grateful for them - because personally, I thought my career was over, but they made sure I took each and every day as it came and made sure that I came here with a healthier mind\\\".\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The South African' is hiring!\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writer positions available.\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us your CV  The draw for Rugby World Cup 2027 will take place in Sydney, Australia on Wednesday, 3 December at 11:00 (SA time).\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3773, \"end\": 3779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999738887211874, \"rank\": 2.611145183572807e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\":